{"tid":2143750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"持BNO網民分享 提前闖英同機12人成功申請LOTR","createTime":"2020-08-07T09:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T14:42:26.000Z","uid":279819,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2863aadffe6a91b3bfd4fd1947e9c4f10aba5323","tid":2143750,"uid":279819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"英國政府早前公布，明年一月起，持英國國民（海外）護照（BNO）的港人和近親，可申請特別簽證。<br />\n因應《港區國安法》實施，英國政府早前公布明年1月起，持英國國民（海外）護照（BNO）的港人及其近親，可申請特別簽證，在此之前入境者亦可申請「Leave Outside the Rules」（LOTR），提早到英國工作及讀書，惟由於英國當局發放的資料不多，不少人擔心未能成功申請。不過，近日陸續有港人在facebook稱已成功能申請LOTR抵英。<br />\n<br />\n英國內政部日前更新LOTR條款，指BNO簽證生效前，建議BNO持有人及其近親以家庭為單位同時入境。facebook專頁「走佬去UK」分享其入境時申請LOTR的經歷，指抵達英國後向關完提出申請LOTR，隨即被暫時沒收護照，經過約半小時的會見問一些簡單問題，例如申請成員之間的關係、工作、財政是否可維持未來在英國的生活等，然後即可領取簽證，整個過程約需兩小時。<br />\n<br />\n網民指，同機12人全部成功申請LOTR，當中包括一名7歲小朋友。<br />\n<br />\n雖然英國政府容許BNO持有人以LOTR形式英國工作及讀書，但不可領取當地福利，明年1月仍需申請專為港人而設的BNO簽證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/politics/article/1339988/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB-%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E6%8C%81BNO%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D%E9%97%96%E8%8B%B1%E5%90%8C%E6%A9%9F12%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8BLOTR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F1339988%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%258C%2581BNO%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25BA%25AB-%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%2597%2596%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%25A9%259F12%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258A%259F%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258BLOTR&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=ce903f1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F1339988%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%258C%2581BNO%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25BA%25AB-%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%2597%2596%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%25A9%259F12%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258A%259F%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258BLOTR&h=65b179a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/politics/article/1339988/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB-%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E6%8C%81BNO%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D%E9%97%96%E8%8B%B1%E5%90%8C%E6%A9%9F12%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8BLOTR</a>"},{"pid":"c7ac3671cd978e935365b589f649a2a3354690ba","tid":2143750,"uid":82588,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:27:39.000Z","msg":"LOTR 應該9成都批，呢過分明係比港人提前走難用。"},{"pid":"cb62822de99faaf31e0b867b78a34e37526260fc","tid":2143750,"uid":154486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:27:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">經過約半小時的會見問一些簡單問題，例如申請成員之間的關係、工作、財政是否可維持未來在英國的生活等</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔係老奉<br />\n要準備好"},{"pid":"1126bc7e4894acf8d0c63a8d2511a3e9be4e2704","tid":2143750,"uid":279819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reT26iz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreT26iz.jpg&h=aaa5710b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nLeave to enter for/until SIX MONTHS <br />\nNo resource to public funds"},{"pid":"ea83541516560d663e4ead1240016e21821d996e","tid":2143750,"uid":92188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:29:53.000Z","msg":"英國今次真係超前部署"},{"pid":"5bbf898590e2a40022b619cdf83f7dea4528ab01","tid":2143750,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:36:11.000Z","msg":"一定要有嚴格審查先可以入英國"},{"pid":"4a204801541546cf5e90e32027d9eb2a6c368b9d","tid":2143750,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"我想問lotr有冇話指定stay喺邊個地方？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901392f8a5e8dc10eb74ab7802642d9abdc46b59","tid":2143750,"uid":67065,"like":1,"di